<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?ish ishref="GUID-A991BC90-EACF-4B07-84D2-8B06129456E2" version="3" lang="en-US"?><concept xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="GUID-A991BC90-EACF-4B07-84D2-8B06129456E2" xml:lang="en-US" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3" domains="(topic concept)                            (topic hi-d)                            (topic ui-d)                            (topic sw-d)                            (topic indexing-d)                            (topic ut-d)                            a(base ishcondition)                            a(base varid)                            a(base varref)                            a(base cid)                            a(base partslist)                            (topic oce-d)                            (topic sdlVariables-c)                            (topic oceCommonElements-c)                            (topic oceMetaDecl-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c concept oceConcept-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c hi-d oceHighlight-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c ui-d oceUi-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c sw-d oceSoftware-c)   " class="- topic/topic concept/concept "><title class="- topic/title ">proCARE introduction</title><abstract class="- topic/abstract " id="GUID-34C6A3E5-E809-4139-80CC-275A8CCF9EDC"><p class="- topic/p ">proCARE is the name of the after-sales service program for the printing system. It offers a unified approach to after sales service, such as spare parts, travel and labor costs, preventive maintenance and application support. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">proCARE offers the customer maximized equipment uptime against clear costs, which maximizes the customers return on their investment. 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Maximized uptime</b> 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Maximize your output. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">The systems unrivaled productivity can be fully harvested thanks to optimally managing the uptime of your printer with proCARE. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Minimize downtime and safeguard steady, continuous production at the highest and consistent quality levels for your system. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Full cost transparency</b> 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">No unpleasant surprises. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Transparent service level of agreements with all related costs ensure that there are no unpleasant surprises: know what to expect, thanks to clear competitive costs. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Highest return of investment</b> 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Realize the lowest Total Cost of Ownership (TCO). 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Do the maths and realize the lowest total cost of ownership over the lifetime of your system. Enabled by the winning combination of an industrial printer with the highest productivity standards and a world class after-sales service program the ensures maximum uptime for the lowest costs. 
</p></li></ul></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Functional description</category></metadata></prolog><conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody "><section id="GUID-99420987-624D-4DD0-B347-3BB55E0CF5B9" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">proCARE options</title><p class="- topic/p ">The table gives an overview of the different flavors of proCARE including the supported options: 
