</p></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table><p class="- topic/p "><sup class="+ topic/ph hi-d/sup ">1</sup> One printhead per year 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">proCARE+ includes all the services of proCARE, adding the entitlement of one printhead replacement per year of term. It also protects against accidental damage of the printhead. It means that if a printhead is damaged by a media crash or due to the wrong manipulation of the operator, it is also protected by proCARE+ (up to one per year). 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">In case of Colorado proCARE+, that annual printhead replacement entitlement can be carried over to the following year, in case it is not used during the year, with a maximum of two replacements in the same year. 
